# Runtime SQLite database — this is live server state, not source. Tracking
# it means every deploy's live data drifts from the last commit, so every
# `git pull` on a running server hits "cannot pull: you have unstaged
# changes" and (worse) a careless stash+pull silently restores an old
# snapshot over the live database. See data/querybot.db removal commit.
data/querybot.db
